## Spec-driven workflow

If this is a spec-driven project (e.g. using GitHub Spec Kit at `.specify/`), see [docs/projects/spec-driven-pattern.md](../../../docs/projects/spec-driven-pattern.md) for the canonical flow.

The TL;DR:
1. Write or update the spec in `.specify/specs/{feature}.md`.
2. Run the spec validator / generator.
3. Hand-edit generated output if needed.
4. Render.

